  <ul>
    <li>Only small islands and territories appear</li>
    <li>No outlines or geographic context</li>
    <li>Subtle shapes, unfamiliar names, and brutal lookalikes</li>
    <li>Designed to expose even advanced blind spots</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Scoring in Extreme mode</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>Maximum score: <strong>2000 points</strong></li>
